## Summary
This documentation details the Airship destination integration with Amplitude, enabling users to sync cohorts from Amplitude to Airship for targeted messaging across channels. It covers setup requirements in both platforms, code samples for linking identifiers, and the process for syncing behavioral cohorts as tags in Airship's messaging system.

